{"tid":1581953,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際特赦組織實地調查指出，香港警方任意拘捕","createTime":"2019-09-19T23:20:05.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-20T14:14:18.000Z","uid":281029,"like":121,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"c68ca36763f531119af2ac6311766be4b25444b5","tid":1581953,"uid":281029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-19T23:20:05.000Z","msg":"【最新調查】國際特赦組織實地調查指出，香港警方任意拘捕、並有證據顯示被捕人士在扣留期間遭受酷刑和其他形式的虐待。國際特赦組織訪問了逾20名被捕人士，並收集了來自律師、醫護人員及其他人士的佐證和證詞。<br />\n<br />\n我們注意到，警方行為有報復心態。被捕人士被打至骨折及內出血﹔有被捕人士表示在扣留期間被警員強行以雷射筆直射眼睛﹔亦有被捕人士表示警方威脅他為電話解鎖，否則電擊其私處﹔更有女示威者表示被祼搜。<br />\n<br />\n此外，綜合我們接觸到的受訪者所言，警方往往拖延5至10小時才應被捕人士要求送院治理，更有以送院為由，威脅他們在沒有律師的情況下落口供。<br />\n<br />\n另外，警方亦以不同理由拒讓被捕人士見律師，包括指電話繁忙、「沒有電話網絡」，又或宣稱警署是「行動範圍」或「警署防線」拒讓律師內進。 <br />\n<br />\n大部份接受國際特赦組織訪問的人士也要求把身分保密，主要是擔心在一片有責不究的氣氛中遭當局報復。有見大眾對監警會等「現行機制」的信任極低，國際特赦組織緊急呼籲香港政府進行獨立、公正的調查，向涉事者提出起訴，彰顯公義，以及為受害人士提供賠償。<br />\n<br />\n全文(只有英文)﹕<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2kv6JXa\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2kv6JXa&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=866674cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2kv6JXa</a><br />\n精讀+新聞稿(中文)﹕<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2kT2J2O\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2kT2J2O&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=cff7a17b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2kT2J2O</a><br />\n精讀+新聞稿(英文)﹕<a href=\"https://www.amnesty.org.hk/?p=18107\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amnesty.org.hk%2F%3Fp%3D18107&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=2973fa13\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amnesty.org.hk/?p=18107</a><br />\n【支持我們繼續跟進調查】<a href=\"https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_s-xclick&amp;hosted_button_id=VBZAJRDFZEECL\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.paypal.com%2Fcgi-bin%2Fwebscr%3Fcmd%3D_s-xclick%26hosted_button_id%3DVBZAJRDFZEECL&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=0c02d487\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.paypal.com/cgi-bin/webscr?cmd=_s-xclick&amp;hosted_button_id=VBZAJRDFZEECL</a><br />\n【成為月捐者】<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2lW48WD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2lW48WD&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=370e0401\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2lW48WD</a><br />\n<br />\n【停止向港售武】<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2M3EBGB\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2M3EBGB&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=5179c7c0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2M3EBGB</a><br />\n【聯合國跟進】人權理事會發言﹕<br />\n41次會議﹕<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2OefLpg\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2OefLpg&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=d622fb30\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2OefLpg</a><br />\n42次會議﹕<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ml7mmw\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ml7mmw&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=61f3cd26\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ml7mmw</a> <br />\n【612警察使用過份武力簡報+改善建議】<br />\n中文全文﹕<a href=\"https://bit.ly/325s1eV\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F325s1eV&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=9aa440ab\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/325s1eV</a><br />\n英文全文﹕<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2ItAdh6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2ItAdh6&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=bf298eb8\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2ItAdh6</a><br />\n手語精讀﹕<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Yyktz5\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2Yyktz5&d=kSOQn%2BAsZtDywzIR1u7IP%2BL6SC4MthnAeNENlMyEb%2BY%3D&h=6624b6fd\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2Yyktz5</a><br />\n互動地圖﹕<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2Iyn9Y1\" data-sr-u